title: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when exporting data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row, an exception is thrown.
EB: The data should be exported successfully without any exceptions.
SR:
1. Add a table to the report that has a group row with a highlight rule and a map rule.
2. Preview the attached report.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
